<?php
return ['messages'=>['#eji-community'=>'#eji-community','#eji-diamonds'=>'#eji-diamonds','#eji-environment'=>'#eji-environment','#eji-metals'=>'#eji-metals','#eji-people'=>'#eji-people','#eji-products'=>'#eji-products','<p>Along the way, we have been monitoring and reviewing our suppliers. The screening is crucial to ensure our suppliers share the same ethical thoughts. We buy most of the diamonds from Sightholder companies and limit our suppliers to only a reasonable number. We know our sources better, we have more confidence in their sourcing operations, and hence our products.</p>'=>'<p>一路上，我們一直在監控和審查我們的供應商。篩選對於確保我們的供應商具有相同的道德思想至關重要。我們從看貨商公司購買大部分鑽石，並將供應商數量限制在合理數量。我們更了解我們的資源，我們對他們的採購業務以及我們的產品更有信心。   </p>','<p>As a certified member of RJC, we commit to operating our business in accordance with the RJC Code of Practices. We are always aware of the transparency and integrity of our supply chain. Nature offers us precious metals and gems, we make huge effort in ensuring our suppliers with ethical and sustainable sourcing. We believe sustainability is a journey, not a destination. We keep looking for ways, big and small, to be a responsible and sustainable jeweler.</p>'=>'<p>作為RJC的認證成員，EJI一直根據準則運營業務，確保供應鏈的透明度和完整性。 可持續發展是一段旅程。   我們不斷尋找各種方式，努力成為負責任珠寶商，在珠寶行業樹立良好榜樣，推動整個行業向更可持續的未來邁進。</p>','<p>As one of Hong Kong’s leading fine jewellery manufacturers, we always have a sincere ambition to be an eco-friendly company.  </p><p>And yet, we faced the toughest challenges to meet the international sustainability standards when we started off our journey a couple of years ago -  when Asia was behind in its push towards sustainability compared to other parts of the world, especially in our industry. Despite where we stand at  times of challenge and controversy, we must make an effort to be more environmentally conscious, no matter how small that impact may be.  </p><p>We focus on putting sustainability at the heart of how we run our business to add value to our company. <br />It is our commitment to being sustainable and ethical jeweller.</p>'=>'<p>EJI作為香港領先的高級珠寶製造商之一，一直立志成為環境友好企業。</p><p>這段旅程充滿挑戰。尤其是亞洲在這方面相較世界其他地區落後。</p><p>儘管如此，我們仍努力於珠寶生產上提高環保意識；將可持續性作為經營核心。</p>','<p>Beyond that, we continue to strive for the best to reduce our impact on the planet. As a pioneer in Hong Kong jewellery manufacturing industry, we believe we are in a unique position to work more sustainably and deliver real impact accross the industry</p>'=>'<p>此外，EJI致力減少對地球的影響。作為香港珠寶製造的領先企業，我們相信可持續運作對整個行業有正面影響。 </p>','<p>Ethical and sustainable sourcing is at the heard of our business.<br />All materials of our responsible jewellery are sourced with the highest ethical standards.</p>'=>'<p>道德和永續的採購是我們業務的核心。<br>我們負責任的珠寶的所有材料均符合最高道德標準。</p>','<p>If you are considering partnering with us, we strongly encourage you to also follow and implement the requirements set by the RJC Code of Practices.</p><p>For more information about RJC, please visit their website at <a href="https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">www.responsiblejewellery.com</a></p>'=>'<p>如果您正在考慮與我們合作，我們強烈建議您也遵循並實施 RJC 行為準則設定的要求。</p><p>有關 RJC 的更多資訊，請訪問其網站 <a href="https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">www.responsiblejewellery.com</a></p>','<p>In the next stage of our path to sustainability, we will continue to pursue our ambitious sustainability agenda in each of our business operations. We are excited to be part of this journey and we believe every small step we take counts to help us achieve our sustainability goal.</p><p>Together, we aim to bring a thriving future for our industry and for our world.</p>'=>'<p>EJI將繼續在每一項業務運作中推進可持續議程。我們相信，每一個小步驟都對實現長久可持續性至關重要。我們將透過與各界通力合作，繼續為珠寶業的可持續發展作出貢獻。 </p><p>我們共同致力於為我們的行業和世界帶來繁榮的未來。</p>','<p>It all started with the raw materials we use. The most important aspects of ethical jewellery production, transparency and traceability of our supply chain, are extremely complicated and difficult to achieve. The Kimberly Process (KP) is one of the ways to seek conflict-free diamonds, and we recognized we had to do more than that and we started to use Know Your Supplier (KYS) solution to help. Working towards transparency and traceability is a real collaborative effort with our suppliers.</p>'=>'<p>一切從原材料開始——EJI只從參與金伯利流程的已知產地採購鑽石。我們確信供應鏈的透明度和可追溯性，是倫理珠寶生產中最重要的面向。<br>過程中，我們持續監控和評估我們的供應商。小心篩選，以確保我們的供應商擁有相同理念。我們從Sightholder公司購買大部分的鑽石，並限制供應商數量。了解原材料來源，令我們對可持續採購及產品品質更有信心。   </p>','<p>Jewellery is a celebration piece of all life’s precious moments to spread joy; a tangible piece of a symbol of family to show love; a sentimental piece that on passes down for generations. Our designs are timeless, and our jewellery is designed for endurance. For us, jewellery can be more than just beautiful. We tried to make a difference to do our business in meaningful ways to give back to our planet. With nothing but a n ethical way in our jewellery production to create sustainable and responsible jewellery.</p>'=>'<p>對EJI來說，珠寶不僅是美麗的象徵。通過採用合乎道德的生產方式，我們力求在作品中體現可持續發展的承諾。<br>環保採購是我們的業務核心。EJI珠寶均以合乎道德的方式採購天然原材料。這不僅體現了我們對環境的承諾，也確保我們的產品合乎社會責任。我們通過小心選擇材料來源，致力推動珠寶行業的可持續發展。    </p>','<p>We are committed to minimizing the impact of our business operations on the environment. We noticed one-time event paper invitations and festive greeting cards leave negative impact on the environment. Think about paper pollution, vehicle pollution during mail delivery, detrimental effects and so on. All these harmful ecological impacts will add up over time, and our planet will pay the price. What we are trying to do is - go paperless. And a better way, why not start to reduce our carbon footprint by stopping the use of paper invitations? Going green is not just a trend. Sending a digital event invite is our first step and we need to start making small changes in any way we can to embrace our environmental responsibilities.</p>'=>'<p>我們致力於最大限度減少我們的業務運營對環境的影響。我們注意到一次性活動紙質邀請函和節日賀卡對環境產生了負面影響。想想紙張污染、郵件投遞過程中的車輛污染、有害影響等等。所有這些有害的生態影響將會隨著時間的推移而累積，而我們的地球將為此付出代價。我們正在嘗試做的是——無紙化。還有一個更好的方法，為什麼不停止使用紙質邀請函來開始減少我們的碳足跡呢？綠色環保不僅僅是一種趨勢。發送數位活動邀請是我們的第一步，我們需要開始以任何方式做出小改變來承擔我們的環境責任。       </p>','<p>We are committed to positively contributing to our community, aiming to build a better tomorrow for our future generations. We actively take part in a wide range of charitable initiatives, including fund-raising events and visits held by NGOs which share the same vision. We are thrilled to engage with youth as we recognize our youth is the hope of our future. Empowering and engaging the youth through various education programs, like sharing sessions and workshops for students in design institutes, are our fundamental work to care and support our community. We will continue to find new ways to give back to the community and keep inspiring our people to pay kindness forward.</p>'=>'<p>EJI致力回饋社區，積極參與各類慈善活動，望為未來世代建立更好明天。我們非常高興能與年輕人互動；透過各類教育計劃，例如為設計學院學生舉辦分享會和工作坊，支持年輕人發展。    </p>','<p>We are proud to be both awarded the “Caring Company” presented by Hong Kong Council of Social Service (HKCSS) and “Happy Company Award” for five consecutive years in recognition of our continuous commitment in building happy caring workplace culture and enhancing happiness-at-work level of our people. Fostering a safe and diversified workplace with equity and dignity is crucial. But we go above and beyond - taking committed actions to provide sustainable employment and build a joyous workplace - to attract, retain and motivate our happy employees. We are dedicated to continuing to care for our people, the greatest asset of our business, and grow together. We believe when our people thrive, our business thrives.</p>'=>'<p>EJI連續六年獲得香港社會服務聯會（HKCSS）頒發的「商界展關懷」和「開心企業」認證，以表揚我們在建立快樂工作文化上的努力。保持一個安全且多元化的工作環境至關重要。我們積極提供可持續的就業機會和愉快工作環境，與員工共同成長。    </p>','<p>We started using certified recycled gold in creating our jewellery pieces from 2019.<br />Creating responsible jewellery is a long arduous journey, especially one made on foot; but we must always remain keenly aware of our responsibilities to the environment. Recycled gold is an extremely effective way to reduce greenhouse gas emissions from mining. We believe the carbon emission savings can be huge. And our hard work paid off - we are proud to be certified as a member of the Responsible Jewellery Council (RJC Certification Number 0000 3707) in 2021.</p>'=>'<p>自2019年起，我們開始使用經過認證的回收金製作珠寶。使用回收金是減少採礦過程中溫室氣體產生的有效方式，亦可減少碳排放。我們的努力得到了回報——EJI於2021年獲得RJC認證（證書號碼 0000 3707），確立了我們在可持續珠寶生產的承諾與努力。   </p>','A team committed to excellence.'=>'追求卓越的團隊。','Empowering and giving back.'=>'回饋社會。','Ethically sourced, expertly crafted.'=>'道德採購，專業製作。','Going green - Not just a trend.'=>'環保 － 不止是潮流。','Our Community'=>'社區','Our Diamonds'=>'鑽石','Our Environment'=>'環境','Our Metals'=>'金屬','Our Next AIM'=>'關於未來','Our People'=>'員工','Our Products'=>'EJI 產品','Our Sustainability Journey'=>'我們的可持續發展之旅','Quality is the priority.'=>'品質至上。','RJC Annual Report 2023'=>'責任珠寶業委員會 （RJC） 2023 年年度報告','RJC Certificate'=>'RJC 證書','Read More'=>'閱讀更多','Responsible sourcing is the key.'=>'致力於負責任的採購。','editor-text-editor-02e4d7f'=>'<p>此外，EJI致力減少對地球的影響。作為香港珠寶製造的領先企業，我們相信可持續運作對整個行業有正面影響。 </p>','editor-text-editor-033fb7e'=>'<p>對EJI來說，珠寶不僅是美麗的象徵。通過採用合乎道德的生產方式，我們力求在作品中體現可持續發展的承諾。<br>環保採購是我們的業務核心。EJI珠寶均以合乎道德的方式採購天然原材料。這不僅體現了我們對環境的承諾，也確保我們的產品合乎社會責任。我們通過小心選擇材料來源，致力推動珠寶行業的可持續發展。    </p>','editor-text-editor-1bbfa9a'=>'<p>如果您正在考慮與我們合作，我們強烈建議您也遵循並實施 RJC 行為準則設定的要求。</p><p>有關 RJC 的更多資訊，請訪問其網站 <a href="https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">www.responsiblejewellery.com</a></p>','editor-text-editor-32bd8d6'=>'<p>EJI連續六年獲得香港社會服務聯會（HKCSS）頒發的「商界展關懷」和「開心企業」認證，以表揚我們在建立快樂工作文化上的努力。保持一個安全且多元化的工作環境至關重要。我們積極提供可持續的就業機會和愉快工作環境，與員工共同成長。    </p>','editor-text-editor-493347d'=>'<p>作為RJC的認證成員，EJI一直根據準則運營業務，確保供應鏈的透明度和完整性。 可持續發展是一段旅程。   我們不斷尋找各種方式，努力成為負責任珠寶商，在珠寶行業樹立良好榜樣，推動整個行業向更可持續的未來邁進。</p>','editor-text-editor-659ca87'=>'<p>自2019年起，我們開始使用經過認證的回收金製作珠寶。使用回收金是減少採礦過程中溫室氣體產生的有效方式，亦可減少碳排放。我們的努力得到了回報——EJI於2021年獲得RJC認證（證書號碼 0000 3707），確立了我們在可持續珠寶生產的承諾與努力。   </p>','editor-text-editor-793c979'=>'<p>EJI作為香港領先的高級珠寶製造商之一，一直立志成為環境友好企業。</p><p>這段旅程充滿挑戰。尤其是亞洲在這方面相較世界其他地區落後。</p><p>儘管如此，我們仍努力於珠寶生產上提高環保意識；將可持續性作為經營核心。</p>','editor-text-editor-797ad5e'=>'<p>一路上，我們一直在監控和審查我們的供應商。篩選對於確保我們的供應商具有相同的道德思想至關重要。我們從看貨商公司購買大部分鑽石，並將供應商數量限制在合理數量。我們更了解我們的資源，我們對他們的採購業務以及我們的產品更有信心。   </p>','editor-text-editor-9348151'=>'<p>我們致力於最大限度減少我們的業務運營對環境的影響。我們注意到一次性活動紙質邀請函和節日賀卡對環境產生了負面影響。想想紙張污染、郵件投遞過程中的車輛污染、有害影響等等。所有這些有害的生態影響將會隨著時間的推移而累積，而我們的地球將為此付出代價。我們正在嘗試做的是——無紙化。還有一個更好的方法，為什麼不停止使用紙質邀請函來開始減少我們的碳足跡呢？綠色環保不僅僅是一種趨勢。發送數位活動邀請是我們的第一步，我們需要開始以任何方式做出小改變來承擔我們的環境責任。       </p>','editor-text-editor-9877af4'=>'<p>EJI致力回饋社區，積極參與各類慈善活動，望為未來世代建立更好明天。我們非常高興能與年輕人互動；透過各類教育計劃，例如為設計學院學生舉辦分享會和工作坊，支持年輕人發展。    </p>','editor-text-editor-c051955'=>'<p>道德和永續的採購是我們業務的核心。<br>我們負責任的珠寶的所有材料均符合最高道德標準。</p>','editor-text-editor-c2f0c99'=>'<p>EJI將繼續在每一項業務運作中推進可持續議程。我們相信，每一個小步驟都對實現長久可持續性至關重要。我們將透過與各界通力合作，繼續為珠寶業的可持續發展作出貢獻。 </p><p>我們共同致力於為我們的行業和世界帶來繁榮的未來。</p>','editor-text-editor-ffbdf02'=>'<p>一切從原材料開始——EJI只從參與金伯利流程的已知產地採購鑽石。我們確信供應鏈的透明度和可追溯性，是倫理珠寶生產中最重要的面向。<br>過程中，我們持續監控和評估我們的供應商。小心篩選，以確保我們的供應商擁有相同理念。我們從Sightholder公司購買大部分的鑽石，並限制供應商數量。了解原材料來源，令我們對可持續採購及產品品質更有信心。   </p>','https://drive.google.com/file/d/1gVs-pCpwW73rr06fMqMzbkXPLMd_IOyt/view?usp=sharing'=>'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1gVs-pCpwW73rr06fMqMzbkXPLMd_IOyt/view?usp=sharing','https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/member/eji-o-b-elegance-jewellery-international-ltd/'=>'https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/member/eji-o-b-elegance-jewellery-international-ltd/','text-button-13ba83b'=>'閱讀更多','text-button-41ceaed'=>'閱讀更多','text-button-6190fbd'=>'閱讀更多','text-button-61de75c'=>'RJC 證書','text-button-7c09bb3'=>'閱讀更多','text-button-8e578f7'=>'閱讀更多','text-button-dd41f2c'=>'責任珠寶業委員會 （RJC） 2023 年年度報告','text-button-e01479b'=>'閱讀更多','title-heading-0b21a91'=>'品質至上。','title-heading-14eb531'=>'金屬','title-heading-2c5037f'=>'員工','title-heading-2f0d59c'=>'社區','title-heading-2f6fc0a'=>'環保 － 不止是潮流。','title-heading-3ad5017'=>'員工','title-heading-490a28c'=>'我們的可持續發展之旅','title-heading-66c359e'=>'追求卓越的團隊。','title-heading-6830fd9'=>'環境','title-heading-6d05114'=>'回饋社會。','title-heading-7116949'=>'EJI 產品','title-heading-7ae16ad'=>'環境','title-heading-7d68576'=>'道德採購，專業製作。','title-heading-7e323e4'=>'致力於負責任的採購。','title-heading-8b5f2de'=>'鑽石','title-heading-9ed4cf8'=>'鑽石','title-heading-b752905'=>'金屬','title-heading-bedac67'=>'EJI 產品','title-heading-dc4daf8'=>'關於未來','title-heading-e8fb947'=>'社區','url-button-13ba83b'=>'#eji-people','url-button-41ceaed'=>'#eji-diamonds','url-button-6190fbd'=>'#eji-community','url-button-61de75c'=>'https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/member/eji-o-b-elegance-jewellery-international-ltd/','url-button-7c09bb3'=>'#eji-products','url-button-8e578f7'=>'#eji-metals','url-button-dd41f2c'=>'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1gVs-pCpwW73rr06fMqMzbkXPLMd_IOyt/view?usp=sharing','url-button-e01479b'=>'#eji-environment']];
